data.title: Joyalukkas Jewellery
data.meta_description: Along with gold, Joyalukkas makes accessories with uncut diamonds, platinum, gemstones and other precious stones. Buy those chokers and earrings to match with prices starting at INR 10,000. You and bae can even go for contemporarily designed "You and Me" rings here.
